{"tid":1224483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6/16 撐警行動","createTime":"2019-06-15T03:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T05:18:45.000Z","uid":1575,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"704cf7acaf1ec7e60c0fdcecb41f03ff28218789","tid":1224483,"uid":1575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"鑑於近日香港出現集體野犬失控成為國際新聞<br />\n本人提議以食物提升警犬士氣：<br />\n<br />\n1）上街人士請每人隨身攜帶狗糧以防不時之需<br />\n<br />\n2）不幸遇上犬隻因天性埋身吠 / 嗅 / 搜，當事人請勿驚恐或刺激犬隻。刺激行為請留給周邊在場人士分散犬隻好奇心<br />\n<br />\n3）滿足犬隻天性後，請拿出狗糧以示友好<br />\n<br />\n4）禮貌分享狗糧給路邊野犬以示鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n5）狗糧並非違禁品<br />\n<br />\n6）想像繁忙時間上街，犬隻被數百路過人士利用食物表示關懷應會令犬隻因天性感到滿足及自豪，激發犬隻狀態"},{"pid":"126585397621f0eb45b465485aa37b1a7eae270b","tid":1224483,"uid":17473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50372a6ebd511dcf4510b4bc2a3ee6f7b1ec453","tid":1224483,"uid":185892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"撐犬行動定撐警行動<br />\n<br />\n算啦都無分別"},{"pid":"8577aa7e3b67b2e6ed57481b98d691fae8054451","tid":1224483,"uid":1575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"相信大部分連登仔都知書識禮受過良好教育及良好市民<br />\n請幫忙宣揚香港和平形象"},{"pid":"652fd4d26484013b6c3467f2e9d9f7f7f32d3373","tid":1224483,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"犬: 你係咪想用狗糧掟我地！"},{"pid":"497ad9b4085537a01adba7d74199476801cf10e1","tid":1224483,"uid":258696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"犬：不要玩食物！"},{"pid":"638f32090283bfe9108aa75f581239e2c7e1565f","tid":1224483,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:41